I"Ç<p>The National Basketball Association (NBA) is a professional basketball league in North America that draws the attention of many basketball fans all over the world. During the regular season, each of the 30 teams (15 in the Eastern Conference and 15 in the Western Conference) plays 82 games. At the conclusion of the regular season, the top eight teams in each conference advance to the playoffs for a chance to compete for the championship title.</p>
